<p>The keywords you’ll probably be looking for are “auto align"</p>
<p>We used path planners on the fly path generation ( <a href="https://www.chiefdelphi.com/t/4915-pathplanner-auto-align-whitepaper/494669" class="inline-onebox">4915 PathPlanner Auto Align Whitepaper</a> ) and found some success with it! Although we didn’t do anything for collision avoidance, rather we just went to the closest side of the reef to minimize the chance of collisions!</p>
